akeake
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:esp. on the Chatham Islands. Also akeake or ake(-)ake, occas. ake (??the main use on the Chatham Islands). Olearia spp. esp. Olearia traversii.  See bastard sandalwood.
Origin:[none]
